# Development guidelines

## Python

Use `uv` to run Python code.

To run anything in Python, use `uv run <command>`.

## Tests

Tests are stored in the `tests` directory.
To run tests run `uv run pytest`


## Alternative way to activate environment

To activate the environment, run `source .venv/bin/activate` as I've `uv venv` to create the environment.